00:50:43,643 --> 00:50:48,325
When it came to selecting your PR firm, how many different firms did you look at?

860
00:50:48,385 --> 00:50:52,786
Do you have any advice for everyone for things to look out for or certain questions to ask?

861
00:50:55,807 --> 00:50:58,147
We interviewed a bunch, then we worked with one for a while,

862
00:50:59,327 --> 00:51:02,568
and then we ended up going with another one based on another recommendation.

