00:54:06,749 --> 00:54:08,290
because there would usually be arguments about,

912
00:54:08,630 --> 00:54:09,970
this is too hard or this isn't too hard.

913
00:54:10,010 --> 00:54:12,531
And then you do the stream and then it's like,

914
00:54:12,831 --> 00:54:14,151
oh, okay, this is, yeah.

915
00:54:14,211 --> 00:54:16,552
So yeah, there was quite a bit of play testing,

916
00:54:16,612 --> 00:54:17,712
not as much as I would have liked,

917
00:54:18,273 --> 00:54:20,793
but there's never enough, but yeah, there was quite a lot.

